{
  "texts": [
    "This problem can be partially mitigated with \"Classifier guidance\".",
    "However, guidance has its limitations too, as the generated reports tend to be of higher quality when the initial diagnostic prediction is also correct (see Supplementary Figure 3).",
    "Another open problem is to find a highly efficient and effective way to encode the positional information of the individual image patches within a WSI.",
    "An interesting research direction is to fine-tune HistoGPT as a conversational chatbot using Reinforcement Learning with Human Feedback (RLHF).",
    "This may prove challenging in practice, as there are currently no slide-level question-answer pairs for the model to learn from."
  ]
}